  "page": "Did you know/109",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that <a href=\"/index.php/Kurleket\" title=\"Kurleket\">Kurleket</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lharys\" title=\"Lharys\">Lharys</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Mohor\" title=\"Mohor\">Mohor</a>, who accompany <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, are a reference to the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Three_Stooges\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Three Stooges\">Three Stooges</a>?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rssm1464.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rssm1464.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/109&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rssm1464.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rssm1464.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <i><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/1464\">The Three Stooges</a></i> (March 10, 2006).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403113316\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU t